{"tid":1610344,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個中國人 國慶做咩好","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:05:36.000Z","uid":112404,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f94f7c5a529855526528c50905265431f5bdbb3","tid":1610344,"uid":112404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"朝早起身睇林鄭av圖 <br />\n早餐食紅雞蛋，一條心，撐紅軍！ <br />\n睇番08奧運劉翔奪冠珍藏版dvd，拎定三卷tempo廁紙，以防睇到衝線一刻走火 <br />\n<br />\nlunch食狗肉<br />\n慶祝今日國慶閱兵，食一餐死一隻台狗，中國統一指日可待<br />\n<br />\n下午gel頭扮盧偉聰，開電腦J光頭sir/朱經偉/暗角柒警<br />\n<br />\nJ完換我愛中國衫落街，買包蒙牛(中國sponsor美斯飲品)，飲到嘔嘔地。 <br />\n<br />\n晚飯係全日重點，著住全套中國紅衫紅褲，手持中國國旗，去美國領事館地址，大唱國歌共5555次，5字=5000億美元關稅。 <br />\n<br />\n晚上安然跳上中國國旗床單睡床，準備夢見全國人大代表夢遺！"},{"pid":"8274eaade8832cde042ae133c59a18bf604a8d82","tid":1610344,"uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"08年係扮傷退賽喎 仲扮中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f369e7e41589f85e6227bb7304e5e7c1a982591","tid":1610344,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"樓主回應下？"},{"pid":"3a8694652da4ce9dacd459c650f3c074bf8495f7","tid":1610344,"uid":112404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8274eaade8832cde042ae133c59a18bf604a8d82","tid":1610344,"uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"08年係扮傷退賽喎 仲扮中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:43:05.000Z","msg":"sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71417612f5fffa83661aba793fce9bc34ee08733","tid":1610344,"uid":112404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f369e7e41589f85e6227bb7304e5e7c1a982591","tid":1610344,"uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTim